{"tid":298832,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【不自量力】謝霆鋒選拔高手挑戰各地頂級廚師 Back選單留名","createTime":"2017-06-26T14:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T04:14:47.000Z","uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cba9de70f9cd28d00fa8193fe730f2c8f7547760","tid":298832,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T14:52:49.000Z","msg":"型男謝霆鋒的烹飪節目《鋒味》系列收視不俗，日前謝霆鋒在社交網發布一段《鋒味》宣傳片，以一句「二百萬創業獎金等緊你」吸引民間烹飪高手加入他的團隊拍攝新一輯《鋒味》節目。霆鋒表示由昨天起（6月25日）上傳烹飪片段到社交網，並在片段上標籤他，他將會在所有參加者中挑選60名入圍者，參與8月在上海舉行的選拔賽，然後8名出線者可以跟他一起到世界各地與不同頂級廚師挑戰，最後3名優勝者便能得到二百萬創業基金。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2sIVs6K\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2sIVs6K&d=cHB5jyzH%2BO0d22hICkGRnjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=319f9385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2sIVs6K</a>"},{"pid":"2f23daae1f7d6f692e3d206e1f9a616761ba0c43","tid":298832,"uid":3037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T14:56:34.000Z","msg":"又衝出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5fb81e7240d156aa4e396fbab6cc90ca772700","tid":298832,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T14:57:55.000Z","msg":"有冇入可以貼返個幾張chok gif出黎"},{"pid":"fd4ca7f092f7aad3ce561bd74e524ec0c47a46a1","tid":298832,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:05:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>8名出線者可以跟他一起到世界各地與不同頂級廚師挑戰</blockquote><br />\n根本就想搵人笨"},{"pid":"3897306d5bdc8fea1263266f166351302a29b87d","tid":298832,"uid":46342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:05:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d14aadc6b54c5b65e1f45df2ed30fc8252440dc","tid":298832,"uid":68547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:06:29.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<span style=\"color: green;\">綠帽男</span>"},{"pid":"3cd1216311fdfa7e2849f72e17ae8b3384c12fff","tid":298832,"uid":2992